<div class="help-content-wrap"><h3 id="sportybingo">SportyBingo</h3>
<ol>
<li><p>SportyBingo is a sort of a &quot;Lucky Draw&quot; game. Prizes of SportyBingo are distributed as Cash. To be eligible for the lucky draw, customers must purchase shares of a given item.</p>
</li>
<li><p>Each purchased share will correspond to a given number. If a customer has purchased 11 shares, this means that the customer also has 11 corresponding numbers attributed to each share. These can be viewed in the customer&#39;s orders.</p>
</li>
<li><p>When a lucky draw of an item starts, a lucky number will be generated. The lucky number will be generated as follows:</p>
<p> (a) Every item has a total of X purchasable shares.</p>
<p> (b) Above generated number is moded by total share number of this prize and the remainder plus one is the final lucky number.</p>
</li>
<li><p>The holder of a share with the same number as the lucky number will be the winner of this item!</p>
</li>
</ol>
</div>